The paper deals with a problem in mobile robotics, specifically place recognition, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves using LiDAR intensity to create a new descriptor, which is related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions the use of a probabilistic algorithm, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves processing natural language, which is related to computational linguistics (cs.CL).
